    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/baeb37f1f5b99d533cab1674d0e890dd.avif?t=1765740084\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/f196e65baf973c5212b0b0e75dee4a00.poster.avif?t=1765740084\" width=616 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/f196e65baf973c5212b0b0e75dee4a00.webm?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/f196e65baf973c5212b0b0e75dee4a00.mp4?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被遗弃在森林深处，<strong>格蕾特和汉塞尔</strong>必须使出浑身解数才能活着回家。一路上，他们将面对狡猾的谜题、邪恶的生物，以及一个无所不知、永不满足的女巫。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/143279b67390f6abba4a4da61f431e2f.avif?t=1765740084\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/289ab7239e3789d6b4fa84604298d563.poster.avif?t=1765740084\" width=616 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/289ab7239e3789d6b4fa84604298d563.webm?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/289ab7239e3789d6b4fa84604298d563.mp4?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《格蕾特与汉塞尔》</i>为玩家“奉上”超过50种独特的死亡动画——有些荒诞，有些令人毛骨悚然。在这里，死亡并非失败，而是乐趣的一部分。事实上，死亡可能会揭示秘密、解锁宝藏或开辟新的道路。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/7647467d3b8f74f05e9eed2c30874033.avif?t=1765740084\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/3326aba340d81ff8bddce176763df78f.poster.avif?t=1765740084\" width=616 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/3326aba340d81ff8bddce176763df78f.webm?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/3326aba340d81ff8bddce176763df78f.mp4?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备上格蕾特可靠的<strong>弹弓</strong>，点击变成了射击。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打破窗户。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戏弄松鼠。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惹恼你的兄弟。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >醒来后发现自己<i>真的</i>不该有的东西……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个高度互动的世界奖励好奇心、恶作剧和跳出思维定式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/07a10aae9badce76eeaa5d2ab392c179.avif?t=1765740084\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/c5c8771ec97966f9062829142cbbe102.poster.avif?t=1765740084\" width=616 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/c5c8771ec97966f9062829142cbbe102.webm?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/c5c8771ec97966f9062829142cbbe102.mp4?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由<strong>数百幅原创水彩画</strong>精心绘制而成，每个角色、树木、阴影和魔法咒语都经过细致的绘制，并在一个丰富的2.5D世界中栩栩如生。结果如何？一个令人难忘的童话故事跃然纸上——既美丽又诡异。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/34b331cb33efb26a7641755aa8b6d07f.avif?t=1765740084\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《格蕾特与汉塞尔：第一部》和《格蕾特与汉塞尔：第二部》最初分别于2009年和2010年发布，游玩次数超过470万次，并在发布后荣登Newgrounds排行榜榜首。如今，15年后，这个扭曲的童话故事以全新的面貌回归——完全重新构思，全手绘，并加入了期待已久的《第三部》。准备好迎接这款备受粉丝喜爱的游戏的回归吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/e9f8b89b557473ffefeca935e353b17c.avif?t=1765740084\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50+ 种动画死亡场景</strong> – 恐怖、搞笑，或两者兼具。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50+ 套服装</strong> – 部分服装可赋予特殊能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20+ 种弹弓</strong> – 火焰、冰霜、烟花等等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+ 个仙女代币</strong> – 解锁全新秘密和额外内容。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抚摸机器人狗狗！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戳熊！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对你的邪恶双胞胎。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抱抱兔子！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >闯入生日派对。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来一场斗舞！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/67dfef13c332494903c88331b5786a3c.poster.avif?t=1765740084\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299820/extras/67dfef13c332494903c88331b5786a3c.webm?t=1765740084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p>",
